618
00:44:09.284 --> 00:44:10.284
Aaron.

619
00:44:10.451 --> 00:44:11.451
Sara.

620
00:44:12.829 --> 00:44:13.829
Stanna där.

621
00:44:36.144 --> 00:44:37.578
Blunda.

622
00:44:37.979 --> 00:44:39.872
- Jag vill inte.
- Gör det.


